ajinkya@hcl-rapid-platform:~/python-clients/Shell-scripting$ ./command_line_args.sh "Ajinkya Dudhal" 29
My name is Ajinkya Dudhal and my age is 29.
2                  # Number of command line args
Ajinkya Dudhal 29  # Command line args as separate strings
Ajinkya Dudhal 29  # Command line args as a single string
